{"tid":1998464,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【黃店】旺角奶路臣街 有黃店小菜攤","createTime":"2020-05-02T11:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T12:56:19.000Z","uid":278414,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"05707a867e62b550aeb4e67a7cf963c15b5bf3d9","tid":1998464,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/64uz0d5cd8jhu4e/status/1256549959471468549?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F64uz0d5cd8jhu4e%2Fstatus%2F1256549959471468549%3Fs%3D21&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=dd5344b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F64uz0d5cd8jhu4e%2Fstatus%2F1256549959471468549%3Fs%3D21&h=8460f173\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/64uz0d5cd8jhu4e/status/1256549959471468549?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n（轉貼）<br />\n<br />\n【#黃色經濟圈 】<br />\n<br />\nFor會自家煮的手足<br />\n#旺角 奶路臣街有 #黃店 小菜攤。<br />\n（下圖紅格附近）<br />\n<br />\n小菜攤貼有 #五大訴求缺一不可  文宣🔥<br />\n由一對年輕男女打理，專賣本地菜👍<br />\n大家有機會就黎幫襯支持一下同路人（買左斤菜心🥬），<br />\n同時可以慢慢戒食大陸重農藥菜。<br />\n(健康第一🙂)<br />\n<br />\n#五一黃金週<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xv3gQ56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxv3gQ56.jpg&h=fd13efac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6AFKZZs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6AFKZZs.jpg&h=27133455&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccdc20eafc8d4d8d495ab35bff9fdfa59de96432","tid":1998464,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2c78cb0f2f3da4f62b1b34d489d3b8e66cc909","tid":1998464,"uid":107366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:51:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid